The 1.10.1 is available up at sourceforge.  Its a bug fix release to 
address the below listed issues:

[ 1563592 ] ARCWriter constructor had its public access removed
[ 1560782 ] StripWWWNRule does not work as advertised
[ 1558157 ] JNDI registration fails in 1.10.0
[ 1566041 ] In 1.10.0, ARC serialno starts at 1 rather than 0

Yours,
